# M85: repo EOL hygiene. Windows checkouts previously got CRLF and every edit
# risked an LF<->CRLF flip (PR #8 staged a ~45-line change as 3000+ lines until
# normalized). All text files are LF in the repo and in checkouts.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.tgz binary
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
